column1: If you publish information from this calculator, please link to and credit LegendCup.com
If Title and Artist are "#N/A" it means that no Title or Artist exist with the chosen Offset 1 and Offset 2 values.
If Offset is "Yes" you can use a number between 0 and 59 in each Offset index.
If Offset is "No" the Min/Max ranges can be ignored as they will not be applied.
